(This is a list of files loaded by boot.rpl on startup.  The base directory
 and extension are automatically added. )
{ "builtins"	(All our safe-to-use types, which should be loaded first.)
  "rpl" 	(The standard library and REPL.)
  "cobs" 	(Codswallop Objects, an OOP implementation.)
  "colors" 	(Beauteous type highlighting.) 
  "colorruntime"(Nicer single stepper and error handler.)
  ("dirtest")	(Directory testing.) }